works.description: Absolut is serving with the best of the vodkas since 500 years and is amongst world’s most expensive vodkas available across the globe. After rolling out vodkas like Absolut Bling or the Swarovski crystals vodka bottle, the company is yet again rolling out an amazing piece of excellence. Travel retail Pernod Ricard has announced the launch of new super-premium vodka Absolut Elyx.
